repo.name: CamPath
repo.description: Path-finding Web app that helps students who are new to a college or university navigate to and from their classes with ease. CamPath takes in a campus map and calculates distances through weighted-nodes that push the finding algorithm closer to the target endpoint. *Prototype from DemonHacks 2019 in collaboration Khaja Ameenuddin, Marco Gutierrez, and Jack Broncato.
